text: Narela Vidhan Sabha Constituency is one of the 230 constituencies of Madhya Pradesh. It comes under Bhopal district. In Narela Vidhan Sabha all major parties including BJP and Congress will fight election face to face. The other parties that is BSP, samajwadi party and Aam Aadmi Party are also in the race. There are also some local political parties in the narela election 2018. Vidhan Sabha narela is the most difficult and important seat for the political parties to won. The main competition is in vidhan sabha narela seat as the headquarter Bhopal Seat.
